### Test Daily Reward Endpoint

# Замініть YOUR_JWT_TOKEN на реальний JWT токен користувача
# Замініть localhost:3000 на ваш сервер, якщо потрібно

### Claim Daily Reward
POST http://localhost:3000/activity/claim-daily-reward
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get User Profile (to check hasReceivedDailyRewardToday)
GET http://localhost:3000/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

###

### Get User Activities (to see daily reward activity)
GET http://localhost:3000/activity/user?skip=0&take=10
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

###

### Get Filtered Activities - Earned (to see daily reward in earned activities)
GET http://localhost:3000/activity/user-profile-activity?filter=earned&period=day
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
